  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc7\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 24 \u0bae\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd - \u0bae\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Attack on empty-faced protestors within 24 hours of President Ranil's inauguration - Maithiri",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Within 24 hours of the inauguration of President Ranil Wickremesinghe, the attack on the empty-faced protestors is strongly condemned.",
        "Former President Maithripala Sirisena has issued a statement saying that during my regime, protests would intensify in Colombo at least 3 times a week and the army was never used to control the protests.",
        "Reassuring the country is important when the people of the country are facing great inconvenience due to scarcity of food, shortage of fuel and gas.",
        "It will never be acceptable to attack the empty-faced protestors in a merciless manner while expecting international cooperation.",
        "During his presidency from 2015 to 2019, there were protests every week in front of the Presidential Secretariat and in the vicinity of Colombo. The military was never used to quell the protests.",
        "During my regime, when the university students and politicians were involved in the protest, the authorities conducted smooth negotiations with the protestors under the guidance of the police. In the case of the Syedum Medical College, all the university students' union would be involved in the protest in Colombo three times a week.",
        "I and the current Justice Minister Vijayadasha found the best solution to the Sitam issue. It is necessary to hold talks with the protesters and preserve the political presence in a democratic manner. There are many evidences that all problems can be resolved through negotiations. We cannot accept that this kind of situation has occurred within 24 hours of President Ranil Wickremesinghe taking office."
      ],
